                                    <p id="resume-gone">
                                        <strong>I am not able to find my resume. It seems to be gone. Why has it disappeared?</strong>
                                        â€‹There can be various reasons why you can't see your resume at first after opening our platform.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        The first one can be that you are probably signed out of your profile.
                                        If you see a button labeled 'Login' in the upper right corner of the screen that means you are logged out of the website.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        Another reason for this could be that you have created more than one different accounts in the platform and that you are currently logged in the wrong one.
                                        Most of the times this is caused by a confusion that if you have an email account by us with a password and use the facebook or linkedin buttons for login you will be logged into that particular account, which is wrong.
                                        The first time you use the facebook or linkedin buttons and give the permissions in the next window a new account will be created for you in our platform, pre-filled with the data we can collect from these social networks.
                                        This is because most of the times the email addresses you are registered with in these social networks are different than the one you use to register an email account with password by us
                                        and simply because most of our users want to have more than one account without registering with a new email address for these profiles.
                                        When you use these social buttons for the second time you will be logged in the corresponding account in our platform.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        If none of the above cases seems to be your's than probably we are experiencing some technical problem
                                        or maybe there is something else that is wrong with your account and you should contact us so we can check what is wrong and get it fixed.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="contact-us">
                                        <strong>How do I get in contact with you?</strong>
                                        The recommended way to get support and help from us, if you already have an account,
                                        is to log into it and use the Intercom integration chat we offer by clicking the question mark icon on a black background in the lower right corner of your screen.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        Otherwise to get in touch with us you can write to us at <a href="mailto:hello@enhancv.com">hello@enhancv.com</a> for whatever reason any time of the day.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        If you are interested in backing us please use this email address: <a href="mailto:invest@enhancv.com">invest@enhancv.com</a>.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        If you are writing about us and want some extra info use: <a href="mailto:media@enhancv.com">media@enhancv.com</a>.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="account-delete">
                                        <strong>How can I delete my account?</strong>
                                        If you want to remove your profile by us,
                                        you have to first log into it from the login popup window then go to this link: <a href="https://app.enhancv.com/settings" target="_blank">My Account</a>.
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        Once you are there and you scroll down to the bottom of the page and you'll see a 'Delete account' button.
                                        After clicking it, you'll have to confirm the delete by writing the word DELETE in the input and clicking the 'Terminate' button and your account will be deleted permanently.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="resume-examples">
                                      <strong>Where can I find some examples resumes?</strong>
                                      You can find some example resumes and get inspired here: <a href="https://enhancv.com/examples.html" target="_blank">Examples</a>.
                                      <br>
                                      <br>
                                      There are also examples appearing for most of the different sections in our platform in the main left toolbar under the section 'Current Example'.
                                      You can also view the full resume examples under the section 'Get Inspired' in the same toolbox of the editor by clicking on the resume thumbnail image.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="student-verify">
                                      <strong>I am not able to verify my student email account? How do I use the student plan?</strong>
                                      If your university student email doesn't bare a domain ending in .edu then you have to write to our support
                                      and provide an university email domain that is valid for all students of this university or faculty and we will add it to our registers.
                                      <br>
                                      <br>
                                      Once your university's email domain is added to our records, you can start inviting your fellow students.
                                      When you reach the required registered students count, which you can view from the platform while inviting, the student plan will be unlocked for all people in this university or faculty.
                                      The sooner you reach the count the sooner the plan will be unlocked for all students.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="mobile-version-msg">
                                      <strong>I am on my desktop computer and I am still seeing the message 'Mobile version is coming soon'. Why and how do I fix this?</strong>
                                      In most of the cases this means that you have to open the site in fullscreen.
                                      This is a message that gets shown when there isn't enough space available in the window to display the editor properly.
                                      <br>
                                      <br>
                                      Your window should not be resized and it should be spanned to full width and height if possible
                                      because the resolution of your computer is not good enough to provide enough space to accommodate the resume editor properly and since we still do not offer a mobile version, for the time being, this is the only option to work with our platform.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="resume-onboarding-data">
                                      <strong>Is the information I choose in the beginning about my field of work and education related to a resume template and content I will get later?</strong>
                                      No. The information you choose in the onboarding screens is used by us for demographic information and customer analysis purposes only
                                      and for now has no effect over the type of resume template or information that get's initially loaded into it.
                                    </p>
                                    <p id="having-doubts">
                                      <strong>All good just having second thoughts if I should use this or stick to using a normal plain resume/CV. What are the benefits?</strong>
                                      If you are having doubts about using a platform of this sort here are some the key points that you can benefit from by creating a resume with it:
                                      <br>
                                      <br>
                                      - Enhancv helps you create performance-based resumes that unveil the real person behind them by using more expressive sections and visual elements that are easily readable and more comprehensible than just plain text;
                                      <br>
                                      - Enhancv helps you customize your resume to each job you are applying for and triple your interview chances;
                                      <br>
                                      - Enhancv gives you valuable tips & examples. Our guidelines summarize some of the best career advice out there from some of the most influential talent managers, career coaches and entrepreneurs;
                                      <br>
                                      - Enhancv lets you add your personal touch by customizing your resume design the way you like it most;
                                      <br>
                                      - Enhancv's smart text analyzers instantly discover all mistakes youâ€™ve made and automatically give you suggestions how to improve them (Coming Soon);
                                      <br>
                                      - After polishing the content of your resume you can download and save it as a .pdf file which is the preferred resume format by most of the companies out there;
                                      <br>
                                      - Enhancv's resume format is readable by most Applicant Tracking Systems, as it was built upon the most-used guidelines.
                                    </p>
